content: {'id': 'be086ff5-cf88-3740-89a6-c689ae2dd507', 'contentType': 'STORY', 'title': 'Nestle India considering price hikes to counter commodity inflation, executive says', 'description': '', 'summary': 'Nestle India will consider raising prices of its products by a small margin to counter inflation in coffee, cocoa and edible oil while aiming to keep sales coming in, a top executive said on Monday.  Profits at Corporate India came under pressure in the October-December quarter due to the double whammy of consumers cutting back due to inflation in large cities and high prices of commodities.
